{"tid":2208971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣軍方︰解放軍19架軍機上午飛越台海中線","createTime":"2020-09-19T10:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T12:11:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9773f688d5148df42a85bbcb1c1dc6ac109e6690","tid":2208971,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550524-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550524-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=eb4a7fe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550524-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d1b81908\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550524-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣軍方表示，解放軍上午共有19架軍機，飛越台海中線，進入台灣西南及西北空域，台方軍機緊急升空作出廣播驅離，並以防空飛彈追蹤監控。<br />\n<br />\n台方表示，解放軍連續2天派出多架軍機飛越台海中線，嚴重破壞台海及區域和平穩定現狀，對此表達嚴正譴責，呼籲北京當局自制，懸崖勒馬，不要成為麻煩製造者，應該共同維護台海與印太區域和平與安全。"},{"pid":"5935c6dd6d84b1df842adccf83752901b752d5e3","tid":2208971,"uid":85629,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:37:01.000Z","msg":"你話支那唔敢打，事實<br />\n<br />\n倒返轉，支那就係知道佢架飛機點飛都好，你亦都唔敢射佢落嚟；亦都睇死台灣唔會派一架飛機做佢同樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78865801f94646eb06ca03e4e6a27a708d2588eb","tid":2208971,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5935c6dd6d84b1df842adccf83752901b752d5e3","tid":2208971,"uid":85629,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:37:01.000Z","msg":"你話支那唔敢打，事實<br />\n<br />\n倒返轉，支那就係知道佢架飛機點飛都好，你亦都唔敢射佢落嚟；亦都睇死台灣唔會派一架飛機做佢同樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"台灣唔敢，但美帝敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3a0